\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(22\)]\) become identities and \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\
\(R\), \(44\)]\) becomes redundant:\>\"", "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"For", "[", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "=", "dimL"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "\[LessEqual]", "dimH"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "++"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"If", "[", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"!", 
         RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "==", "3"}]}], ",", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
        RowBox[{"Print", "[", 
